  "title": "拿下 30 个第 1 名的腾讯混元翻译模型，开源！",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkwODU2OTQyNQ==&mid=2247495898&idx=1&sn=794059ae679330749643795a3d560939",
  "date": "2025-09-01 10:28:00",
  "author": "腾讯混元",
  "siteName": "腾讯混元",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span></span></p>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=53269b54&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F9u3YmmgmjbTtQXIntL3YWkmylwpEiblgib0G4VyBHsIpX5KibmdlGiaQYibRyA5lSVvAWwto90upKGEKOBNicAS5uD8Q%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">今天，我们带来一个在国际机器翻译比赛拿下30个第1名的翻译模型</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Hunyuan-MT-7B，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">它</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">总参数量仅7B，支持33个语种、5种民汉语言/方言互译</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，是一个能力全面的轻量级翻译模型。&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6810035842293907\" style=\"width: 564.74px;height: 384.59px;\" data-w=\"2232\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=14343fb2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F9u3YmmgmjbTtQXIntL3YWkmylwpEiblgibb5ks42ibbEAuJ9LHvMAPib6swjvkE2HWIFHpWyUbd5QL5Ik9oEykkoNw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">同时开源的还有一个翻译集成模型&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Hunyuan-MT-</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Chimera-7B （奇美拉）</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，是业界首个翻译集成模型，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">它能够根据原文和多个翻译模型给出的不同内容，再生成一个更优的翻译结果，不仅原生支持</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">Hunyuan-MT-7B，也支持接入 deepseek 等模型</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，对于一些有专业翻译需求的用户和场景，可以提供更加准确的回复。</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"3 3 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><o:p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">相比传统的机器翻译，基于大模型的翻译对于对话背景、上下文内容以及综合的翻译需求有更深度的了解，进而能够提供更加准确和“信达雅”的翻译，这也为翻译模型的落地应用打下了基础。我们看看</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Hunyuan-MT-7B翻译的几个实际例子，真正做到了又快又准。</span></span></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><o:p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">首先是俚语翻译：</span></span></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><o:p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">然后是古诗翻译：</span></span></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">还有带有缩写的社交对话翻译：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在8月底结束的国际计算语言学协会（ACL）WMT2025比赛中，腾讯混元Hunyuan-MT-7B（参赛名称：Shy-hunyuan-MT）</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">拿下了全部 31个语种比赛中的30个第1名，处于绝对领先地位</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，这 31个语种除了中文、英语、日语等常见语种，也包含捷克语、马拉地语、爱沙尼亚语、冰岛语等小语种。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <v:shapetype coordsize=\"21600,21600\" path=\"m@4@5l@4@11@9@11@9@5xe\" filled=\"f\" stroked=\"f\">\n    <v:formulas>\n     <v:f eqn=\"if lineDrawn pixelLineWidth 0\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"sum @0 1 0\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"sum 0 0 @1\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"prod @2 1 2\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelWidth\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelHeight\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"sum @0 0 1\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"prod @6 1 2\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelWidth\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"sum @8 21600 0\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelHeight\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"sum @10 21600 0\"></v:f>\n    </v:formulas>\n    <v:path gradientshapeok=\"t\"></v:path>\n   </v:shapetype>\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.9770290964777948\" style=\"width: 433.07px;height: 423.19px;\" data-w=\"1306\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=35a94358&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F9u3YmmgmjbTtQXIntL3YWkmylwpEiblgibnG7SpK2I8ic4lia10HyEWKU8yb4UKic0g0MS2VFDe7eib3t2ThtVtHTcDw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></span>\n  </p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">图：在WMT2025官方提供的成绩报告中，腾讯混元“shy-hunyuan-MT”即Hunyuan-MT-7B模型拿下了全部31个语种比赛中30个第1名，以上是英语-简体中文翻译的得分情况。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><o:p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">WMT25竞赛对参赛模型的参数规模有明确限制，要求系统满足开源要求，并且只能使用公开数据进行训练，在这样的环境下，Hunyuan-MT-7B击败了众多参数更大的模型。</span></span></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5741849634065203\" style=\"width: 604.74px;height: 347.23px;\" data-w=\"3006\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=21d14f16&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F9u3YmmgmjbTtQXIntL3YWkmylwpEiblgibwicickB3478CvLicIcT0SdzWRxeXxQcJCH9uib4jmRhibWqz3CNpmFlL1dQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">图：同尺寸模型下，Hunyuan-MT-7B效果领先于业界顶尖模型</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5918774966711052\" style=\"width: 604.74px;height: 357.93px;\" data-w=\"3004\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ee7e963e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F9u3YmmgmjbTtQXIntL3YWkmylwpEiblgibSnjAIgGicBQASic91SGj0Dic0pZJj2Kf5Sr7Kics1v55l8J4EPINuqdnpA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">图：Hunyuan-MT-7B效果与超大尺寸模型效果对比也不逊色</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><o:p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在业界常用的翻译能力测评数据集&nbsp;</span></span></o:p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Flores200上，腾讯混元</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Hunyuan-MT-7B模型也有卓越的效果表现，明显领先于同尺寸模型，与超大尺寸模型效果对比也不逊色。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><o:p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">取得全面领先的成绩，离不开技术上的全面突破，针对翻译场景，腾讯混元提出了一个完整的翻译模型训练范式，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">覆盖从预训练、到CPT再到监督调参、翻译强化和集成强化全链条</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，使得模型的翻译效果达到业界最优。&nbsp;</span></span></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <v:shapetype coordsize=\"21600,21600\" path=\"m@4@5l@4@11@9@11@9@5xe\" filled=\"f\" stroked=\"f\">\n    <v:formulas>\n     <v:f eqn=\"if lineDrawn pixelLineWidth 0\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"sum @0 1 0\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"sum 0 0 @1\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"prod @2 1 2\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelWidth\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelHeight\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"sum @0 0 1\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"prod @6 1 2\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelWidth\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"sum @8 21600 0\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelHeight\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\"sum @10 21600 0\"></v:f>\n    </v:formulas>\n    <v:path gradientshapeok=\"t\"></v:path>\n   </v:shapetype>\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3547351524879615\" style=\"width: 566.33px;height: 202.83px;\" data-w=\"1246\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0a41ef27&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F9u3YmmgmjbTtQXIntL3YWkmylwpEiblgibia2ac87aZaGqeZzN7jac0THg7Iic5B4Qx19XMc8P6p21o0LXia23WfTIA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></span>\n  </p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Hunyuan-MT-7B的特点在于仅用少量的参数，就达到甚至超过了更大规模模型的效果，这也为模型的应用带来了众多优势。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">首先是计算效率，7B模型的推理速度明显快于大型模型，在相同硬件条件下能够处理更多的翻译请求，并且，基于腾讯自研的AngelSlim大模型压缩工具对Hunyuan-MT-7B进行FP8量化压缩，推理性能进一步提升30%。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">其次是部署友好性，Hunyuan-MT-7B能够在更多样化的硬件环境中部署，从高端服务器到边缘设备都能良好运行，并且模型的部署成本、运行成本和维护成本都相对更低，在保证翻译质量的前提下，为企业和开发者提供了更具吸引力的解决方案。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><o:p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">目前，腾讯混元翻译模型已经接入腾讯多个业务，包括</span></span></o:p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">腾讯会议、企业微信、QQ浏览器、翻译君翻译、腾讯海外客服翻译等，助力产品体验提升。</span></span><span style=\"font-family: minorHAnsi;font-variant: normal;text-transform: none;\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><o:p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">自2023年亮相以来，腾讯混元积极拥抱开源，通过开放自研技术，推动大模型技术的共享和突破，在推出翻译模型之前，已经陆续开源了业界领先的文生文、文生图、视频生成和3D生成能力和相关工具集插件，提供商业模型性能的模型服务，相关模型多次登顶开源社区热度榜榜首。未来，腾讯混元还将开放更多模型和技术，和社区携手，共建开放大模型生态。</span></span></o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Hunyuan-MT-7B 模型已在腾讯混元官网上线体验入口，并在Huggingface和Github等开源社区提供下载，对应的技术报告和论文也已经在开源社区公开，欢迎体验和下载。</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">体验地址：<a href=\"https://hunyuan.tencent.com/modelSquare/home/list（文末阅读原文直达）\" target=\"_blank\">https://hunyuan.tencent.com/modelSquare/home/list（文末阅读原文直达）</a></span></span><span style=\"font-family: minorHAnsi;font-variant: normal;text-transform: none;\"></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Github: <a href=\"https://github.com/Tencent-Hunyuan/Hunyuan-MT/\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/Tencent-Hunyuan/Hunyuan-MT/</a></span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">HugginFace: <a href=\"https://huggingface.co/collections/tencent/hunyuan-mt-68b42f76d473f82798882597\" target=\"_blank\">https://huggingface.co/collections/tencent/hunyuan-mt-68b42f76d473f82798882597</a></span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align:left;line-height:1.3;margin-top:3pt;margin-bottom:3pt;text-indent:-16.8pt;margin-left:16.8pt;margin-right:0pt;mso-list:l0 level1;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;mso-font-width:100%;\" data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\">Angel</span></span><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;mso-font-width:100%;\" data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\">Slim</span></span><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;mso-font-width:100%;\" data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\">压缩</span></span><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;mso-font-width:100%;\" data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\">工具</span></span><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;mso-font-width:100%;\" data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\">：</span></span><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0pt;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-style:normal;mso-font-width:100%;\" data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://github.com/Tencent/AngelSlim\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/Tencent/AngelSlim</a></span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "腾讯混元开源了其在 WMT2025 比赛中斩获 30 项第一的轻量级翻译模型 Hunyuan-MT-7B，并发布了业界首个翻译集成模型 Hunyuan-MT-Chimera-7B。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "腾讯混元开源了其在 WMT2025 比赛中斩获 30 项第一的轻量级翻译模型 Hunyuan-MT-7B，并发布了业界首个翻译集成模型 Hunyuan-MT-Chimera-7B。",
  "summary": "文章宣布腾讯混元正式开源其机器翻译模型 Hunyuan-MT-7B 和 Hunyuan-MT-Chimera-7B。Hunyuan-MT-7B 是一款参数量仅 7B 的轻量级模型，在 WMT2025 国际机器翻译比赛中，于 31 个语种中斩获 30 个第一，超越了众多参数更大的模型。该模型支持 33 种语言和 5 种民汉方言互译，在俚语、古诗等复杂语境下表现出色。同时开源的 Hunyuan-MT-Chimera-7B 是业界首个翻译集成模型，能整合多模型结果以生成更优翻译。文章强调了 Hunyuan-MT-7B 在计算效率和部署友好性上的优势，并通过腾讯自研 AngelSlim 工具实现 FP8 量化压缩，推理性能提升 30%。这些模型已应用于腾讯会议、企业微信等内部产品，并已在 Huggingface 和 Github 等平台开放下载，体现了腾讯积极拥抱开源的策略。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "腾讯混元 Hunyuan-MT-7B 在国际机器翻译大赛 WMT2025 中表现卓越。",
      "explanation": "该 7B 参数模型在 31 个语种中斩获 30 个第一，在受限条件下超越众多大参数模型，证明了其先进性和高效性。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Hunyuan-MT-7B 在多语种支持和翻译质量上实现全面突破。",
      "explanation": "模型支持 33 种语言和 5 种民汉方言，能准确翻译俚语、古诗等复杂语境，提升了翻译的“信达雅”水平。"
    },
    {
      "point": "业界首个翻译集成模型 Hunyuan-MT-Chimera-7B 提升专业翻译准确性。",
      "explanation": "该模型能整合多个翻译结果生成更优输出，尤其适用于专业翻译场景，为用户提供更高质量的翻译服务。"
    },
    {
      "point": "轻量级设计使得模型在计算效率和部署友好性上优势显著。",
      "explanation": "7B 模型推理速度快，配合 FP8 量化压缩进一步提速 30%，可在多样化硬件环境部署，大幅降低运行和维护成本。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "Hunyuan-MT-7B，它总参数量仅 7B，支持 33 个语种、5 种民汉语言/方言互译，是一个能力全面的轻量级翻译模型。",
    "Hunyuan-MT-Chimera-7B （奇美拉），是业界首个翻译集成模型，它能够根据原文和多个翻译模型给出的不同内容，再生成一个更优的翻译结果。",
    "在 8 月底结束的国际计算语言学协会（ACL）WMT2025 比赛中，腾讯混元 Hunyuan-MT-7B（参赛名称：Shy-hunyuan-MT）拿下了全部 31 个语种比赛中的 30 个第 1 名，处于绝对领先地位。",
    "Hunyuan-MT-7B 的特点在于仅用少量的参数，就达到甚至超过了更大规模模型的效果，这也为模型的应用带来了众多优势。",
    "目前，腾讯混元翻译模型已经接入腾讯多个业务，包括腾讯会议、企业微信、QQ 浏览器、翻译君翻译、腾讯海外客服翻译等，助力产品体验提升。"
  ],
